{"tid":100763,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同令一半行到緣盡","createTime":"2017-01-30T09:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T18:03:10.000Z","uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c26bf8542bcaa5f1a6f991264bdf4e0e278ec935","tid":100763,"uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"大家都好似覺得由愛情變到感情<br />\n<br />\n四年時間大家都認真左唔少心機建立互信 磨合<br />\n<br />\n互相見過幾次家長 亦都幻想過對方就係岩既人<br />\n<br />\n最後大家和平分手 <br />\n<br />\n其實就冇咩遺憾 只不過好似浪費女方幾年最美麗既青春歲月 <br />\n<br />\n經過依次好似大過左 唔會再隨便拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後當然係希望令一半find a better man<br />\n<br />\nPs. 其實好灰 求巴絲打吐下苦水<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927b6dacff877d18ca9c26421f89d529fc52f6ee","tid":100763,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"Same case<br />\nSame feeling<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e73ac83514558e9cf52901f29bdba2682c9f75","tid":100763,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:02:29.000Z","msg":"我好驚會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a17c4b2a9f7c51d22eb62a658884ae81b5c6aad","tid":100763,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家都好似覺得由愛情變到感情<br />\n<br />\n四年時間大家都認真左唔少心機建立互信 磨合<br />\n<br />\n互相見過幾次家長 亦都幻想過對方就係岩既人<br />\n<br />\n最後大家和平分手 <br />\n<br />\n其實就冇咩遺憾 只不過好似<span style=\"color: red;\">浪費女方幾年最美麗既青春歲月</span> <br />\n<br />\n經過依次好似大過左 唔會再隨便拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後當然係希望令一半find a better man<br />\n<br />\nPs. 其實好灰 求巴絲打吐下苦水<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br /